### Test Duties API Integration

# Get all duties
GET http://localhost:3000/api/duties
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

# Get duties with date filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/duties?date=2024-01-15
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

# Get duties with date range filter (startDate and endDate)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/duties?startDate=2024-01-15&endDate=2024-01-20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

# Get duties with startDate only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/duties?startDate=2024-01-15
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

# Get duties with endDate only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/duties?endDate=2024-01-20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

# Get duties with duty type filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/duties?dutyType=TRIP
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

